Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.63,0:01:45.82,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你还是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:49.19,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我还是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:55.52,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}倘若能彼此交心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:02:03.86,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自那天起 四季更替时光流转
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:09.65,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我只想说 谢谢你伴我至今
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:17.86,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}呵着白气 朝向狭窄的小巷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:23.25,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你温暖的手使劲拉着我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:25.21,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不断前行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:28.41,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}好想马上就亲吻你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:32.11,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}躲在自动售货机背后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:35.56,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}害羞地凝视对方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:41.00,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}温柔的心情洋溢胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:44.53,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你还是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:47.98,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我还是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.32,0:02:53.42,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}倘若能彼此交心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:55.57,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我们便能融为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:58.77,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}与一份小小幸福的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:02.32,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}似乎就在触手可及的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.52,0:03:05.05,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}能变得如此温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:08.01,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}全因有你
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------EDCN5-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.28,0:22:14.96,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,150)\be1}心儿一紧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.07,0:22:18.53,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)\be1}这感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.55,0:22:22.86,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)\be1}是坠入爱河的证据吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:33.67,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}在小小的草坪上 玩耍嬉戏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.76,0:22:39.26,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}那是幼时纯真的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.32,0:22:45.23,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}但我却渐渐感受到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.32,0:22:49.56,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}心底那不断膨胀的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.67,0:22:55.95,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}和你相处那么久
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.08,0:23:00.12,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}都无法向你坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:03.53,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}总是绕远路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.00,0:23:09.50,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,150)\be1}在心里紧紧地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.87,0:23:11.93,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)\be1}在你身旁静静地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.97,0:23:18.20,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,150)\be1}抱住你 凝视你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.58,0:23:23.46,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}那是小小爱恋的开端
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.59,0:23:27.51,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}虽然此刻还无法开口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.52,0:23:31.47,EDCN5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1}我喜欢你
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------PREV-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.86,0:00:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家注意不要受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听从执行委员的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.91,0:00:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把东西收拾好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.89,0:00:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创设祭也顺利结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的杂烩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校友们都说 是游泳部的传统味道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七咲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本食谱 我想托付给你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是该给二年级的学姐么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要给我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 希望你能收下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那萝卜的味道相当棒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 比不上学姐的海带
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.23,0:00:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七咲 你要继承这本食谱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.80,0:00:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后继续守护游泳部的传统味道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.04,0:01:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小逢 明年也多煮点我最喜欢的鱼糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.86,0:01:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会跟响来吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来不来还是未知数哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样 来吃鱼糕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.57,0:01:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梨穗 你那边搞定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.04,0:01:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～基本上搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.81,0:01:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉时间过得太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.25,0:01:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.75,0:01:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…是学姐叫我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帮了忙 表示感谢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝天之下饮茶品茗　不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺风雅的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,品尝风雅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃荆棘之途
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 总比大热天冒着烈日喝茶强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 特意跑到外面大费周章
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有风情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱慕风情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃修罗之道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 被炉果然是天堂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梨穗 快要在被炉扎根了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也会举行野外茶会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.77,0:04:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 初春时会这样来招新哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 之前都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为比较土 基本上新生也不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年还因为下雨中止了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精心准备的茶点剩了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.43,0:04:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也挺麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 唯一加入的某部员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将它们清理得十分干净
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:05:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得野外茶会挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.47,0:05:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是放点音乐说不定会更好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不过 这就不算享受自然了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的主意很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 明年开始试试这样做也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托一下吹奏乐部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们跟我们一起搞招新活动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 小梨穗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们明年也会来看的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 明年春天学姐们都毕业了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计会冷清下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会守护茶道部的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 收拾一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 对茶有兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 弄起来相当难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶道很深奥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 实在弄不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一 换我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎跟学姐们完全不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子跟我没大差别嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了学姐 我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走了～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 回去时小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意防摔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～再…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.66,0:06:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话音未落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么华丽地回应了期望啊 小梨穗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年也拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:07:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 小梨穗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾东西辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.44,0:07:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶道部的茶会很热闹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天给你们添麻烦了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝甜酒能醉成那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计也只有老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 明年请你要注意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惩前毖后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会注意的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执行委员长真能干
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梨惠能有她一个指甲盖强就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能有一个肚脐眼强也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然到25日了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.64,0:07:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能三个人聚在一起开圣诞派对真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟美也是连续两天派对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们 这么为我着想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这蛋糕和菜肴都是中多带过来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 跟爸爸说今天要来美也家开派对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就准备了这些 让我带过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大个蛋糕吃得完吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.58,0:08:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕不占空间～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天收到你们的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天轮到我回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.44,0:08:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有时间么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是在减肥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我点东西 你只喝水这也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子也点一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是刚才在活动室吃了那么多点心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不控制一下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样看着 我都不好意思吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吃一半哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行 我要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不要用那种眼神看着蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡要续杯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞也要打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除夕和元旦倒是能休息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年到31号我都跟妈妈一起大扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备年夜饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后到零时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去年初参拜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 要跟我说什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实啊 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:10:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你说的回礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 想到要什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 呃…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去年初参拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过这样就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那31号晚到我家来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是要吃蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是香苗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 香苗在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 那边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到减肥中的你还在吃蛋糕的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会很生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 在那里嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.47,0:10:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 纯一就会骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你之前还叫我帮你减肥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天吃下去的 过后会好好运动的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动量会比平常多很多的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话啊 电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥 电话！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说有电话啦 老哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道 马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也 怎么穿成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家还在洗澡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.64,0:12:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷啊 快点接
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿梅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美少女为了接我的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,围着条浴巾从浴室飞奔过来～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒假可以过来借那部新片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊 啥时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看除夕怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.44,0:12:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索性直接到你家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开「好片鉴赏会」得了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选出年度最佳好片也挺有搞头的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还要玩之前说的新射击游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 除夕我没时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好了要跟梨穗子去年初参拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你这叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛什么徒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好意思说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然跟樱井去年初参拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们什么时候变成那种关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了 竟然瞒着我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:12:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再冷淡点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟梨穗子只是普通的青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥们 你知不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱井其实很受欢迎的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还收过男生的情书
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福意外地近在咫尺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.72,0:13:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 我刚才很有诗意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.05,0:13:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 可以算金句了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 要么今天来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想问你借些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约到他啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺行的嘛 樱井
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是不错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有个不好的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜的蛋糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 纯一说给我吃 就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:14:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我准备做运动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃过以后再运动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 加油吧 樱井
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标…100个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…没力了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟纯一去年初参拜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 美也去开门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也 不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 美也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 梨穗子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 纯一真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得真早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好久没跟美也好好聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃过年荞麦面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 差不多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.49,0:15:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近老哥会主动泡茶了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前都不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐教了我怎么泡好茶嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点上瘾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一泡得比我好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热水的温度和焖的时间很有讲究的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是泡好茶的要点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拽什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦 两位不要因小事吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.15,0:15:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 吃这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挑战了一下新菜单
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.44,0:15:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝士蛋奶酥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 看上去很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝士蛋奶酥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的减肥计划呢 梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这蛋奶酥是减少糖的份量的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得芝士的卡路里很高吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 这…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 这个真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多到唱歌节目的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的压轴是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用问 当然是小纱布啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.99,0:16:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 今年那个偶像组合要登场哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也也喜欢么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 小梨穗好有型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 挺不错的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.36,0:17:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们只有演艺圈出道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入演艺圈就有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然喜欢唱歌 不过当偶像就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…也没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥 给我电视遥控器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在你那边么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 当了偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能像现在这样过除夕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 差不多要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过美也睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿她没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先去准备一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子 帮忙叫美也起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也 美也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 准备OK
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 准备OK
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 人没叫醒自己也睡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄豆面也不错 花生酱也很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.81,0:18:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 做梦也想着吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:19:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱井现在应该跟橘在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年初参拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一 美也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床起床 睡过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很空呢 说不定还算好运呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.11,0:19:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零点前后来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计要排上1小时左右的队才能参拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来考高中时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是跟纯一来这里祈祷合格的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子做数学题时老是会睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子 第二问做好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.59,0:20:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 记得是暑假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼 休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼 休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.55,0:20:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼 休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果老是分神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果老是吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 最后还是考上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写上愿望 再挂在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:21:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是已经心里有数了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}（希望减肥成功 有新人加入茶道部）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥 小梨穗 来抽签吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小吉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是末吉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.45,0:21:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,末吉和小吉哪个更好运？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来末尾的末 应该就是最后了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是{\fnMS Gothic}末広がり{\r}（逐渐兴盛）的末
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是比较好的意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.89,0:21:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下退下 大吉大人要过路了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你玩什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有善哉粥（加入年糕的小豆粥）哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.44,0:21:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:21:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善哉粥啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过正月嘛 吃了也没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.51,0:21:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 你说什么 纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:22:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨穗子应该吃没加年糕的善哉粥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)\fad(0,450)}那就称不上善哉粥了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.70,0:22:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)\fad(450,1200)}（希望心意相通）
