Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.11,0:23:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到新年了呢 小梨穗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.01,0:23:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.08,0:23:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 今年也多…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 今年我们要毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.54,0:23:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.20,0:23:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糊涂小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.39,0:23:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.48,0:23:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.71,0:24:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点收到新部员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.15,0:24:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要收的只是新部员吗～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.36,0:24:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.21,0:24:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令～
